Package org.pepstock.charba.client.adapters

Class NativeDateAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pepstock.charba.client.adapters.NativeDateAdapter
  • @JsType(isNative=true,
        name="CharbaChartAdaptersDate",
        namespace="<global>")
final class NativeDateAdapter
extends Object
    It maps a date adapter of CHART.JS.
    An adapter is the reference to an external date library.
    Author:
    Andrea "Stock" Stocchero
